<p></p>
<p><strong>Includes:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Roundtrip airfare from Salt Lake City</li>
<li>All ground and air transportation within Europe</li>
<li>All accommodations during the trip</li>
<li>Admission to castles, museums, attractions, concerts, etc.</li>
<li>Some meals</li>
</ul>
<p></p>
<p><strong>Does not include:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Tuition for classes</li>
<li>Passport application fees</li>
<li>Overweight baggage fees</li>
<li>Most meals</li>
<li>Personal expenses and souvenirs</li>
</ul>
<p>When considering the cost of the trip, figure the cost of one semester block at BYU-Idaho (housing, food, entertainment, etc.). Deduct this amount from the cost of Experience Europe, and the trip becomes much more cost effective. In addition, our special group rates allow you to get a lot of travel for your dollar. In addition, any financial aid you will receive for Fall Semester can be applied to the trip.</p>
<p><strong>Payment Schedule</strong></p>
<p>If you are accepted on the trip, your BYU-Idaho account will be charged the full $3,995. A $500 non-refundable payment to your account is due by May 15, 2014 to secure your space on the trip. Failure to make this payment will result in cancellation of your reservation for the trip. The remaining $3,495 will be due on or before September 1, 2014.</p>
<p>In case of cancellation you will lose the non-refundable, $500 payment as well as any additional costs incurred at that point in the planning and preparation for the trip. <strong>There are no exceptions to this policy.</strong></p>]]></BodyCopy><xPower Type="GroupStart" Name="PageComponents" label="Page Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="true" GroupStart=""><xPower Type="List" Name="OptionalColumnComponent" label="Optional Column Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="true" List=""><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="Optional" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="false"/></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Name="QuickLinksColumn1" label="QuickLinks Column 1" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Name="QuickLinksColumn2" label="QuickLinks Column 2" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Name="QuickLinksColumn3" label="QuickLinks Column 3" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent" Expanded="false"/></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Name="HighlightedLinks" label="Highlighted Links" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="x8228" CompTypes="HighlightedLinksComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="List" Name="ContentSnippet" label="Content Snippet" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false" List="xpowercomponent_ContentSnippet"><xPower Type="Component" Name="ContentSnippet" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="ContentSnippet"/></xPower><xPower Type="Navigation" Name="AncestorNavigation" label="Ancestor Navigation" readonly="true" hidden="true" required="false" Expanded="false" Naviga